description: Martel Yggdrasill was http://anidb.net/ch16628 [Mithos Yggdrasill]`s older sister. She helped her brother Mithos, together with http://anidb.net/ch11682 [Kratos Aurion] and http://anidb.net/ch11714 [Yuan Ka-Fai], to end the Ancient Kharlan War over 4000 years ago.
